, does he tell that to all the devotees in ISKCON?"}, {"start": 276.3, "end": 276.5, "text": " No."}, {"start": 276.94, "end": 277.08, "text": " Then?"}, {"start": 280.66, "end": 286.04, "text": " Yes, for their level it is good. You chant, better you become, you know, think of the"}, {"start": 286.04, "end": 294.34, "text": " qualities of Jesus Christ. You will get purified. Think of what is Allah. Allah, you just see"}, {"start": 294.34, "end": 295.04, "text": " all the..."}, {"start": 295.44, "end": 303.06, "text": " You take Vishnu Sahasranama and somewhere I read a thousand names of Allah. All almost"}, {"start": 303.06, "end": 308.62, "text": " same. He is omniscient, omnipotent, this, that, he is detached, he is compassionate, all"}, {"start": 308.62, "end": 313.7, "text": " compassionate, all transcendental. All this, this is a meaning of Allah, a thousand names"}, {"start": 313.7, "end": 314.04, "text": " of Allah."}]}